QALD question: What is the location of the wine production of Sparkling wine?
QALD SPARQL query:
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> 
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri

        ?uri dbo:location res:France .
